snippet: Serena Williams began her bid for a ninth Miami Open title by beating Christina McHale, 6-3, 5-7, 6-2, in Key Biscayne, Fla....
lead_paragraph: Serena Williams began her bid for a ninth Miami Open title by beating Christina McHale, 6-3, 5-7, 6-2, in Key Biscayne, Fla.
abstract: Top-seeded Serena Williams wins her opening match against Christina McHale in Miami Open; Williams is seeking her ninth title at Key Biscayne, Fla, event.

headline.main: Serena Williams Opens Bid for 9th Florida Title
headline.print_headline: Williams Opens Bid for 9th Florida Title
